    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《幸存者计划》是一款弹幕地狱类、群体幸存者类动作游戏，除了生存和获得升级之外，您还必须完成每个任务的目标，才能在这个反乌托邦世界中前进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/4ca4349a792652cef91cda914651bd1f.poster.avif?t=1752526264\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/4ca4349a792652cef91cda914651bd1f.webm?t=1752526264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/4ca4349a792652cef91cda914651bd1f.mp4?t=1752526264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成目标，同时抵御一波又一波的敌人，他们会试图在精神上阻碍你解锁新的地点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/1513ff0940e797fc881fc753d4709fc0.poster.avif?t=1752526264\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/1513ff0940e797fc881fc753d4709fc0.webm?t=1752526264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/1513ff0940e797fc881fc753d4709fc0.mp4?t=1752526264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >该游戏最初的设计将包括 3 种游戏模式：战役（或历史）、生存和撤离。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/629d26fc8e43ffc0d9d09673467dac6a.avif?t=1752526264\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras_big/629d26fc8e43ffc0d9d09673467dac6a.avif?t=1752526264 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包括许多不同的地图：未来关卡、当代环境、幻想地点等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >环境差异的原因是什么？时间旅行？平行世界？开发人员抽了一支巨大的小岛秀夫烟吗？也许吧。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/263f8039cca2e38f589d72d6fc002cd7.avif?t=1752526264\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras_big/263f8039cca2e38f589d72d6fc002cd7.avif?t=1752526264 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >众多角色拥有不同的能力来对抗坏人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角色都有一种或多种对敌人造成的伤害类型和独特属性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >杀死更多敌人，获得更多经验并收集更多分子以变得更强大（通过购买更多东西）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/d27f9b5c397a35c3ed2f787a4102df9f.poster.avif?t=1752526264\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/d27f9b5c397a35c3ed2f787a4102df9f.webm?t=1752526264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/d27f9b5c397a35c3ed2f787a4102df9f.mp4?t=1752526264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角色都有 6 种不同的武器可供获取（手枪、步枪、武士刀、刀、霰弹枪等）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数百种角色/武器/技能组合供您选择，因此当您死亡时，您可以责怪游戏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >改进和可访问性</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>改进</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/697a642bdf05beeb5381482288933b2b.poster.avif?t=1752526264\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/697a642bdf05beeb5381482288933b2b.webm?t=1752526264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/697a642bdf05beeb5381482288933b2b.mp4?t=1752526264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >召唤（近战、远程、健康等）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >区域爆炸</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冲击波</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轨道</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >十字（正面和对角线）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正面</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >背面</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多个</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >等等</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>无障碍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用辅助功能系统配置难度，以便您享受或感到沮丧，您选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/05fe5460686147f3937dd7a8d407c667.poster.avif?t=1752526264\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/05fe5460686147f3937dd7a8d407c667.webm?t=1752526264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/05fe5460686147f3937dd7a8d407c667.mp4?t=1752526264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特征</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自拍。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速游戏（如果用双手玩，则不超过 20 分钟）。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >众多具有不同能力的角色可以与坏人战斗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数百种角色/武器/技能组合供您选择，因此当您死亡时可以归咎于游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在躲避一波又一波试图使您精神短路以解锁新地点的敌人的同时完成目标。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >杀死更多敌人，获得更多经验并收集更多分子以变得更强大（通过购买更多东西）。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/60fa6de4cf4b2968b1f0d43a4534a1a2.poster.avif?t=1752526264\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/60fa6de4cf4b2968b1f0d43a4534a1a2.webm?t=1752526264\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3083190/extras/60fa6de4cf4b2968b1f0d43a4534a1a2.mp4?t=1752526264\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
